{"tid":2281824,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"《LegCo 101》楊岳橋立會生存真人show！","createTime":"2020-11-11T11:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T13:35:02.000Z","uid":140060,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a46fa694836d8dfe7059721ea437e9796ad2bb","tid":2281824,"uid":140060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"　　在不久的未來，全球除香港以外全部陸沉。<strong>人類的命運由名為「中共」的神秘組織所掌握。</strong>為了拯救法治，民主與糧資，黃絲律師兼手足<ins>楊岳橋</ins>參加了「中共」舉辦的生存遊戲&mdash;<strong>立法會選舉。</strong><br />\n<br />\n　　<strong>贏得立法會選舉，就可以繼續於議會抗爭，督眼督鼻，永續爭取民主。</strong>在選舉中，岳橋遇到了昔日的隊友，若薇，家傑，還有一眾老對手，佩帆，美芬等人，<strong>他們既是敵人，又是同事，於議事廳內惺惺相惜。</strong><br />\n<br />\n　　<strong>好景不常，在選舉中途，「中共」突然宣布新規矩：每週會DQ一位議員，篩走不合「阿爺」心意的參賽者。</strong>岳橋眼見其他議員一個一個被DQ，仍深信法治有險可守，<strong><span class=\"large\">Over My Dead Body！</span></strong>而且，他們搞港獨，阿爺當然不喜歡了，被先DQ也是咎由自取。<br />\n<br />\n　　但隨著民主派議員一個一個被DQ，連與自已出生入死的老伙伴家傑也被DQ，岳橋的心態開始動搖；為求苟廷殘喘多一兩個回合，<strong>他甚至向國安舉報若薇，凱迪，之鋒搞港獨，並繼續安撫黃絲支持者：法治有險可守，</strong><strong><span class=\"large\">Over My Dead Body！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n　　選舉進入尾聲，建制派議員竟退出遊戲，另一個神秘組織「人大」借松泰的軀殼向岳橋招手；<strong>食碗面反碗底的岳橋，心靈逐漸瓦解，常常喃喃自語：</strong><strong><span class=\"large\">Over My Dead Body⋯</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n　　在喪失理性的邊緣，岳橋在信箱收到了一部瑞麟錄音機，<strong>聽到了頌恆和蕙禎「被消失」前的口訊，更於夢到天琦讓他選擇紅色和藍色藥丸，加入地下革命組織本民前⋯</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>成為體制的齒輪，或是全力反抗，岳橋最終會否拯救法治</strong>，並且令龍威及Cyber City不用執笠⋯？</span></span>"},{"pid":"1ad25674ed64d0ae9d152cbd0b6d3080581dabcc","tid":2281824,"uid":196326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2355734d1e0777457901e92564a0da7d5897c07","tid":2281824,"uid":282347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:42:59.000Z","msg":"第一集：師父的叮嚀<br />\n<br />\n預告：岳橋正當不知所措之時，人稱十一哥的師父渣華約他到家見面，更道出了雪廠街的往事，竟有著意想不到的一面⋯⋯"},{"pid":"f8da6b34ea16eda85fef45249e0ca12984fceabe","tid":2281824,"uid":140060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cf79e45dd588551ac663aab582041d820479bbb","tid":2281824,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529855e470646da51aecd2101fb55ad30cea9722","tid":2281824,"uid":140060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4207cbb64031335a7236c5964d7d8188f8c0bc36","tid":2281824,"uid":140060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ec00cc98224fbaae33178a255f3f7bebba68148","tid":2281824,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20170710/NI3ZTNDTGZLX7LVCYA7HQLN5AM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20170710%2FNI3ZTNDTGZLX7LVCYA7HQLN5AM%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVERZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=d66d2448\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20170710%2FNI3ZTNDTGZLX7LVCYA7HQLN5AM%2F&h=4ad4f9ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20170710/NI3ZTNDTGZLX7LVCYA7HQLN5AM/</a>"},{"pid":"e04ad86aa20816ae2cc97e9bbdcc22e1f034a221","tid":2281824,"uid":140060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a25d2cda85ddbbf213f7e2478694d678256e86a4","tid":2281824,"uid":140060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2efcf649a62cc45c61f5515408b20da1cb46f6e","tid":2281824,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB